meback thereafter int he battle)<br>3. comeback (in open battle i use comeback as main style and ravager as backup style)<br>4. /stick<br>5. ravager (see 3. coemback)<br>6. atrophy (follow up of 5)<br>7. scathing blade (follow up of 6)<br>8. /face (when i am following a target, but cant restealth, I use face like a radar to find him.)<br><br>Hotkey bar 4: (my frontstab bar, with 2h start and switch to 1h left axe)<br><br>Obvious - I switch to two 1h weapons asap to apply all my nifty poisons. I sacrifiece melee damage, but got my poisons in effect asap.<br><br>1. stealth<br>2. perforate artery<br>3. mainhand 1h weapon hotkey<br>4. /stick<br>5. offhand 1h weapon hotkey<br>6. Creeping death<br>7. Stunning Stab<br>8. /face<br><br>Hotkey bar 5: (my backstab bar, with 2h start and switch to 1h left axe)<br><br>Similar comment to hotkey bar 4.<br><br>1. stealth<br>2. BAckstab 2<br>3. mainhand 1h weapon hotkey<br>4. /stick<br>5. offhand 1h weapon hotkey<br>6. Thigh cut<br>7. &lt;free&gt;<br>8. /face<br><br>Hotkey bar 6:<br>key 1 and 8 are for PvE. The others are mostly keys for nice effects: like casting DoT with 1035 range while staying hidden,...<br><br>1. throwing daggers<br>2. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>3. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>4. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>5. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>6. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>7. &lt;usable item&gt;<br>8. distract<br><br>Hotkey bar 7: is empty <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Hotkey bar 8: (emoticons.....)<br>When u see a fellow assassin from another realm being ganked by several members of the 3rd realm, you should help him. When battle is over, you both should stealth and laugh and dance =). Same when you investigate collory gates and see a grey. Bow, laugh, dance, wave and leave. Gives greys a nice feeling....<br> <p>But as always: only my five cents ;-)<BR><BR>--- <BR>Gerbrandt Hurricane<BR><BR>LvL 50 Shadowblade, Bors<br> <br>Horus Heresy, Lord Guardian on Europa shard of Ultima Online<br><img src="http://gul.50g.com/images/guardians.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utiejinnie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tiejinnie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/6/02 3:14:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3471.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://homex.coolconnect.com/member3/Tiejinnie/images/Avatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hotkey bar strategies</span><hr size=1> lol, interesting,<br><br>I never knew there was so much knowledge to apply to hotkey bar setup.<br><br>I guess the best setup is one where the player feels the most comfortable with, and is very familiar with.<br><br>As they say, as long as it works for you, anythiing goes! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><fontcolor="cornflowerblue"><i>Tiejinnie<br>Lurikeen NightShade<br>Legion of Avatars - Kay Server</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uphelmich.showPublicProfile?language=EN>phelmich</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/6/02 5:44:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3471.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hotkey bar strategies</span><hr size=1> Regarding:<br><br>Similar comment to hotkey bar 4.<br><br>1. stealth<br>2. BAckstab 2<br>3. mainhand 1h w